org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.handlers.soap
Class AeSOAPMessageWrapper

java.lang.Object
  javax.xml.soap.SOAPMessage
      org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.handlers.soap.AeSOAPMessageWrapper
public class AeSOAPMessageWrapper
extends javax.xml.soap.SOAPMessage

A wrapper around an Axis message. This class exists in order to fix some problems with the Axis implementation of the org.w3c.dom.Element interface.
